  "description": "AECC Aviation Power Co.,Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture, sale, and maintenance of aircraft engines and its parts in China and internationally. The company offers large and medium-sized aero-engines, gas turbines, components, and spare parts; general-purpose equipment and motors; and non-aviation and other products. It also provides maintenance and support; equipment installation; aviation equipment repair; and foreign trade export subcontracting services. The company serves the military and civilian markets. It exports its products. The company was formerly known as AVIC Aviation Engine Corporation PLC and changed its name to AECC Aviation Power Co.,Ltd in March 2017. AECC Aviation Power Co.,Ltd was founded in 1958 and is based in Xi'an, China.",
